  <brief_title>Effect of Walking on Brain Fuel Consumption in Mild Alzheimer's Disease</brief_title>
  <acronym>MAL</acronym>
  <official_title>Evaluating the Impact of Physical Exercise on Mild Alzheimer's Disease in a Randomized Clinical Trial: Quantification With 18F -FDG and 11C- AcAc PET Imaging</official_title>
  <sponsors>
